{"tid":1790753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵：呼籲任何人停止破壞設施","createTime":"2019-12-20T08:38:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T09:23:12.000Z","uid":95138,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9f17451b87f0eb92d414d8801def033898779776","tid":1790753,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:38:49.000Z","msg":"連登仔：唔好亂裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb970a39db3215ee828bdf9c879ef950de2c5e5","tid":1790753,"uid":95138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:39:53.000Z","msg":"大學站明天重開 港鐵表示如有需要會調校列車服務<br />\n2019-12-20 HKT 12:25<br />\n<br />\n港鐵宣布，關閉超過一個月的東鐵綫大學站明日重開，但D出口暫時無法使用。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵公司副車務總監李家潤說，部分設施包括入閘機及升降機仍未修復，開放初期只維持基本服務，又預計D出口需時數個月才能維修好，再次呼籲任何人停止破壞設施、停止任何危害乘客或職員的行為。<br />\n<br />\n李家潤說，已通過風險評估，並與政府部門溝通，判斷明日可以回復服務，若有任何情況，有需要時會調較列車服務、甚至停止服務，有需要時亦會與警方聯絡。"},{"pid":"e49590155f0fb3e6590684298fd87372fdd468a1","tid":1790753,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:40:32.000Z","msg":"止暴制亂就成功 大家要冷靜少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3cf1ffaf32a9129e8aba88a3f22c7fe7956dc1d","tid":1790753,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:41:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1498740-20191220.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1498740-20191220.htm&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5Ysqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=a242d7c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1498740-20191220.htm&h=a66eb342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1498740-20191220.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e190f1d2dbf49cc62e9fd435cc3ed6bc130c5140","tid":1790753,"uid":2924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,